column2: We are fifty or a hundred years behind the rest of the world. We must make up for this in ten.
Start the industrialization of the oppressed!
Fuel the fires of industry! The might of the proletariat shall be forged in the steel flames of our future!

column3: Munch munch is a pussy for speaking French

column2: Build the minds of our youth!
Crush the Fifth Collumn of resistance!
The opponents of the state have bade their time to long--they must be crushed!
We must slay these agitators and operators of disorder!
We must forge our own revolution!
The Right has Struck against us!
Clerks have locked down stores and banks, and keep the worker in poverty!
Bureaucrats have stolen vital papers, burned logs, and hidden vital information while they hide from duty!
The various Counter-Revolutionary forces have blinded the peasants, who now work against us and the revolution!
The bureaucracy is in revolutionary shambles!
